KitKat::
She watched as Drillbit fell to the floor.  She used all her 
strength, but she mamaged to get him into the CR chamber and turned 
it on.

Feline::
She turned and saw how upset HotRod looked as he worked.  She turned 
and faced her bench and smiled. She knew for sure she had him wrapped 
around her little claw.  She walked over to him and kissed his 
cheek. "Ok handsome, you win, let's go back to your room.  Then if 
I'm successful of getting your mind off of 'things' then maybe I'll 
get some work done around here. What do you say?"
